OL,3,CLabour's Claire Ward elected as first
OL,4,Cregional mayor for the East Midlands
OL,6,FThe new mayor will have the
OL,7,Fopportunity to address regional
OL,8,Fissues. Some of Ms Ward's promises
OL,9,Finclude securing better local
OL,10,Ftransport, more investment in the
OL,11,Flocal economy and setting up a
OL,12,Fhomelessness taskforce.
OL,14,FWhat can the East Midlands mayor do?
OL,16,FThe East Midlands mayor will have
OL,17,Fsignificant power over regional issues
OL,18,Fsuch as public transport, economic
OL,19,Fredevelopment, housing and living
OL,20,Fstandards.
