OL,8,Fmore prosperous.
OL,10,FWho is Claire Ward?
OL,12,FMs Ward previously served as an MP
OL,13,Funder Tony Blair and Gordon Brown as
OL,14,Fmember for Watford from 1997 to 2010.
OL,15,FShe also served as a Government Whip
OL,16,Ffrom 2005 to 2009 and a Justice
OL,17,FMinister from 2009 to 2010.
